{"tid":189001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禽流疫區雞翼埋地底　馬來西亞民眾照挖「尋寶」","createTime":"2017-04-06T06:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T04:06:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6c78d2d7f1258f6a295422102ef4abd1c35f24","tid":189001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170406/photo/bknint-20170406125416508-0406_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170406134937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170406%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170406125416508-0406_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170406134937&h=5930c347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾湧到現場挖掘「尋寶」，有即席烤過的雞翼散布在地（小圖）。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞當局早前把一批走私急凍雞翼，埋入砂拉越一處深坑銷毀，雞翼來自曾傳出禽流感疫情的荷蘭。惟不少民眾發現後未有理會雞翼來歷不明，湧到現場挖掘「尋寶」，更疑有人即時烤來吃。當局已封鎖現場防止民眾「盲搶」。<br />\n<br />\n該批急凍雞翼被埋於砂拉越詩巫石山路一處空地下3米深，當地一名居民上周五從友人處得悉，有5輛各載有約27噸重雞翼的貨車駛至，有人把雞翼埋入該處地下。消息傳開後，吸引不少民眾帶工具前去挖雞翼，然後帶回來煮，有人更搭帳篷以便「尋寶」。現場甚至可見，一隻隻已即席烤過的雞翼散布一地。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞皇家關稅局詩巫分局其後確認，這些雞翼都是從荷蘭走私到該國，遭到當局充公及銷毀。荷蘭較早前曾傳出禽流感疫情，故當局去年11月30日起禁止從荷蘭進口禽類食品。詩巫省獸醫局上周四接獲關稅局通知，曾前往檢查該批雞翼的情況。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，關稅局一般以土埋方式銷毀未符標準的肉類，此前會灑上石灰消毒，惟今次未完成此層善後工作。由於該批雞翼可能已受毒物污染，當局呼籲居民扔掉，並於周二傍晚起封鎖該空地，阻止民眾來挖雞翼。由於未確定事件是否涉違法，當地警方仍未展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170406/bknint-20170406125416508-0406_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170406%2Fbknint-20170406125416508-0406_17011_001.html&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b37bf5b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170406/bknint-20170406125416508-0406_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"44e77e541eee19a6921f16b113484956acac27c6","tid":189001,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"智商何在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7b064969b8bfbbb11cb2f305e1311fa7f96659","tid":189001,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"乞衣雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d21974819b851fef4e7dac1c657a18021e0210","tid":189001,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"馬拉狗特別弱智"},{"pid":"089346314918b785fa8c6bf65503eba91ada0f2e","tid":189001,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"馬拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88679fde767b0908be3d4fc31f69a60f4b3ff873","tid":189001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db2c91233a7a5085b7c66ad6069feef0cd89df8","tid":189001,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"同鄰國一撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3abef13f31dfdcbc26f70f94dd1eb99722e74c7","tid":189001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}